c: 34
v: 14
t: "Kodwa Sathi Sisakumisela ukufa kuye (uSulaymân) akwabikho nto izichazelayo ngokufa kwakhe ngaphandle komsundululu womhlaba owawumana ugrenya umsimelelo wakhe Wathi akuwa phantsi, (kwangona) zibonayo iiJinni okokuba ukuba zazikwazi okungabonwayo, ngezazingazanga zihlale (phantsi) kwesohlwayo sokudeleka (okungako)"